## 2. Core Features

### 2.1 Game Window

**Game Framework:** {% if game_framework == 'pygame' %}Pygame 2.5.0+{% elif game_framework == 'arcade' %}Arcade 2.6.17+{% elif game_framework == 'pyglet' %}Pyglet 2.0.0+{% elif game_framework == 'pgzero' %}Pygame Zero 1.2.1+{% endif %}

